					<description><![CDATA[Notification Reminder is one of the helpful feature in Samsung Galaxy S5 that help you to know the unread notifications. This feature also help you to alert/remind you about the unread notifications until you read/open them. This feature is very helpful for people who are so busy that they forget the message/plan in their phone. [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><strong>Notification Reminder</strong> is one of the helpful feature in Samsung Galaxy S5 that help you to know the unread notifications. This feature also help you to alert/remind you about the unread notifications until you read/open them. This feature is very helpful for people who are so busy that they forget the message/plan in their phone.</p>
<p><a href="http://sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Screenshot_2014-12-27-03-48-28-e1419655538641.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-138" src="http://sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Screenshot_2014-12-27-03-48-28-168x300.png" alt="Screenshot_2014-12-27-03-48-28" width="168" height="300" /></a>  <a href="http://sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Screenshot_2014-12-27-03-48-20-e1419655689358.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-139" src="http://sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Screenshot_2014-12-27-03-48-20-168x300.png" alt="Screenshot_2014-12-27-03-48-20" width="168" height="300" /></a>  <img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-213" src="http://sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-03-04-03-46-168x300.png" alt="Screenshot_2015-01-03-04-03-46" width="168" height="300" srcset="https://www.sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-03-04-03-46-168x300.png 168w, https://www.sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-03-04-03-46-576x1024.png 576w, https://www.sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-03-04-03-46.png 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 168px) 100vw, 168px" />  <a href="http://sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-03-17-01-31.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-225" src="http://sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-03-17-01-31-168x300.png" alt="Screenshot_2015-01-03-17-01-31" width="168" height="300" srcset="https://www.sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-03-17-01-31-168x300.png 168w, https://www.sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-03-17-01-31-576x1024.png 576w, https://www.sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-03-17-01-31.png 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 168px) 100vw, 168px" /></a>  <a href="http://sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-03-17-01-07.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-226" src="http://sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-03-17-01-07-168x300.png" alt="Screenshot_2015-01-03-17-01-07" width="168" height="300" srcset="https://www.sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-03-17-01-07-168x300.png 168w, https://www.sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-03-17-01-07-576x1024.png 576w, https://www.sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-03-17-01-07.png 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 168px) 100vw, 168px" /></a></p>
<p>How to use:</p>
<ol>
<li>Swipe down the top of screen to open the <strong>notification panel</strong> and then tap to <strong>setting</strong> icon</li>
<li>From the <strong>setting</strong> function, select <strong>Device</strong> Tag and scroll down to <strong>Personalization</strong> section and then tap to <strong>Accessibility</strong>.</li>
<li>Select <strong>Vision</strong></li>
<li>Select <strong>Notification Reminder</strong> and enable this feature.</li>
<li>After switching on <strong>Notification Reminder</strong> feature, you can set the interval time between alerts by changing the time in <strong>Reminder interval</strong> function.</li>
<li>Complete setting</li>
</ol>
<p>Above steps are used to enable/set the <strong>Notification reminder</strong> feature in Samsung Galaxy S5. Hope it is helpful for you.</p>
